### Go MySQL CRUD — VS Code REST Client
### Install: humao.rest-client extension
### Click "Send Request" above each block

@base = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@id   = PASTE_PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### ─── Health ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET http://localhost:8080/health

### ─── CREATE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Product 1
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MacBook Pro 14",
  "description": "Apple M3 Pro chip, 18GB RAM",
  "price": 1999.99,
  "stock": 25,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

### Create Product 2
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Clean Code",
  "description": "A handbook of agile software craftsmanship",
  "price": 34.99,
  "stock": 150,
  "category": "Books"
}

### ─── READ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all products
GET {{base}}/products

###

### Filter by category
GET {{base}}/products?category=Electronics

###

### Search by keyword
GET {{base}}/products?search=apple

###

### Get single product (paste ID from create response)
GET {{base}}/products/cdd73f28-6e75-4435-83ec-59c6faf171bf

###

### Stats — total products, stock, avg price, categories
GET {{base}}/products/stats

### ─── UPDATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Update product (partial — only send fields you want to change)
PUT {{base}}/products/cdd73f28-6e75-4435-83ec-59c6faf171bf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1799.99,
  "stock": 30
}

### ─── DELETE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete product
DELETE {{base}}/products/10a51459-2134-4b98-b605-8293e3776f62

### ─── Error Cases (try these too) ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Missing required field → 400
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "No name provided"
}

###

### Non-existent ID → 404
GET {{base}}/products/non-existent-id-12345
